trans-unit.source: Represents the method that will handle the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TreeView.BeforeCheck"></xref>, <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TreeView.BeforeCollapse"></xref>, <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TreeView.BeforeExpand"></xref>, or <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TreeView.BeforeSelect"></xref> event of a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TreeView"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 처리 하는 메서드를 나타냅니다는 <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TreeView.BeforeCheck"> </xref>, <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TreeView.BeforeCollapse"> </xref>, <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TreeView.BeforeExpand"> </xref>, 또는 <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TreeView.BeforeSelect"> </xref> 의 이벤트는 <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TreeView"> </xref>합니다.

trans-unit.source: When you create a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TreeViewCancelEventArgs> delegate, you identify the method that will handle the event.
trans-unit.target: 만들 때 한 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TreeViewCancelEventArgs>이벤트를 처리 하는 메서드를 식별 대리자를 실행 합니다.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.TreeViewCancelEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: To associate the event with your event handler, add an instance of the delegate to the event.
trans-unit.target: 이벤트를 이벤트 처리기를 연결 하려면 대리자의 인스턴스 이벤트에 추가 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The event handler is called whenever the event occurs, unless you remove the delegate.
trans-unit.target: 대리자를 제거 하지 않으면 이벤트가 발생할 때마다 이벤트 처리기가 호출 됩니다.

trans-unit.source: For more information about event handler delegates, see [Events](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: 이벤트 처리기 대리자에 대 한 자세한 내용은 참조 [이벤트](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)합니다.
